    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "The land that is now North Merrick once belonged to the indigenous Rockaway and Merrick tribes.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        3
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 2"
      ],
      "source": "https://www.wisdomlib.org/cities/north-merrick-34472"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "Camp Avenue, Jerusalem Avenue, Meadowbrook Road, and Merrick Avenue are historic routes that still define the hamlet’s layout.",
